Dear Jonathon=2C

A definition of =A02-fibration is given in the following sources:Claudio He=
rmida=2C "Some properties of Fib as a fibered 2-category"=2C J. Pure Appl. =
Alg. 134-1 (1999) 83-109.Claudio Hermida=2C "Descebt on 2-fibrations and st=
rongly 2-regular 2-categories"=2C App. Cat. Str. 12 (2004) 427--459.=A0

It is adopted (Definition 4.1) and used =A0in=A0Marta Bunge and Claudio Her=
mida=2C 'Pseudomonadicity and 2-stack completions"=2C Proceedings of the Ma=
kkaiFest=2C CRM Proceedings and Lecture Notes=2C to appear 2011=2C=A0a prep=
rint of which I shall send to anyone requesting it.=A0
Best wishes=2CMarta Bunge


